Get Image

Source: R/get_image.R
get_image.Rd

Get Image

Usage

get_image(tissueSampleId = NULL, page = 0, itemsPerPage = 250)

Arguments

tissueSampleId

Array of strings. A list of Tissue Sample ID(s).

page

Integer (default = 0).

itemsPerPage

Integer (default = 250).

Value

A tibble.
